- `PostResponse getOwn(Long, UserDetails)` — owner only
- `Page&lt;PostSummaryResponse&gt; listOwn(UserDetails, PostStatus, Pageable)` — owner's drafts &amp; published

**PostServiceImpl.java**
- Admins are forbidden from authoring posts
- Uses PostMapper to enrich responses with like counts and user's liked/bookmarked flags
- Supports filtering by category, full-text search, custom sorting
- Increments viewCount on read
- Batch-fetches engagement data to avoid N+1

